    "This observation confirmed the correct positioning of the molecules based on their structural similarities.",
    "Furthermore, an LDA analysis of the green box molecules confirmed that there is a projection that maximizes the distance between different scaffolds even if they are structurally very similar (Additional file 7: Supplementary Fig.",
